10:48:42 AM [express] GET /api/settings 200 in 3ms :: {"designer_name":"Alex Morgan","designer_title":"UX/UI Designer","bio":"I'm a UX/UI designer passionate about creating digital experiences that solve real problems and delight users. My journey into design started 5 years ago when I realized that good design isn't just about aesthetics—it's about empathy, strategy, and impact.","bio_extended":"I believe the best designs are invisible. They guide users effortlessly toward their goals while making complex tasks feel simple. My approach combines user research, data analysis, and creative problem-solving to build products that people actually want to use.","bio_personal":"When I'm not pushing pixels, you'll find me brewing specialty coffee, producing music, or contributing to design communities. I love sharing knowledge and learning from other designers.","years_experience":5,"projects_completed":50,"happy_clients":20,"location":"San Francisco, CA","email":"alex@example.com","linkedin":"linkedin.com/in/alexmorgan","twitter":"@alexmorgan","dribbble":"dribbble.com/alexmorgan","behance":"behance.net/alexmorgan","cv_url":"#","availability_status":"Currently Available","availability_note":"Open for new projects starting February 2026","trusted_companies":["TechCorp","StartupXYZ","DesignLab","InnovateCo"],"skills":["User Research","Wireframing","Prototyping","UI Design","Design Systems","Usability Testing","Information Architecture","Interaction Design"],"tools":[{"icon":"figma","name":"Figma"},{"icon":"adobexd","name":"Adobe XD"},{"icon":"sketch","name":"Sketch"},{"icon":"framer","name":"Framer"}],"beyond_design":[{"icon":"users","title":"Design Communities"},{"icon":"coffee","title":"Coffee Brewing"},{"icon":"music","title":"Music Production"}],"why_work_with_me":[{"icon":"search","title":"Research-driven design","description":"Every decision backed by user research, data analysis, and behavioral psychology."},{"icon":"zap","title":"Fast & scalable systems","description":"Building design systems that grow with your product and accelerate development."},{"icon":"trending-up","title":"Business-focused UX","description":"Balancing user needs with business goals to drive measurable results."}],"avatarUrl":"/uploads/bc3b586b-2347-40ab-bb69-2a63a8169640.jpeg"}
